divs: Sighting DetailsI woke up early in the morning and i was going to get a cup of coffee from allsups when i saw a bright egg shaped object in the sky. My first reaction was "Oh my God". I knew that i had to report it so i decided to come here to report it. Iam still shookin up from what i saw.
